      reflection: "Tetelestai. Paid in full. Not mostly paid. Not paid contingent on my future behaviour. Paid. In. Full. There is therefore now no condemnation. Not 'no condemnation if I keep performing.' No condemnation. This is not permission to sin — it is the power to stop. Because I am not fighting for acceptance. I am fighting from it.",
